# T-B-003 — BBC Learning English Integration (Metadata + Learning Overlay)

## Objective

Integrate BBC Learning English into DriveSmart Listening without copying or storing BBC copyrighted audio/transcript content.

DriveSmart will act as a learning layer on top of BBC content by providing:

* Discovery
* Bookmarking
* Progress tracking
* Learning notes
* Vocabulary collection
* Dictation workspace
* Future AI features

BBC remains the original content source.

---

# Business Goals

1. Expand listening content quickly.
2. Avoid content creation bottleneck.
3. Avoid copyright risks.
4. Improve SEO through topic discovery pages.
5. Increase retention through progress tracking and learning tools.

---

# Non-Goals

Do NOT:

* Download BBC audio files
* Rehost BBC audio
* Store BBC transcripts
* Republish BBC content
* Clone BBC pages

DriveSmart is a companion learning platform.

---

